{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#4394: CSS @import and background-image path not resolved in Custom Elements",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:27:20.901629+00:00",
  "text": "CSS @import and background-image path not resolved in Custom Elements\n\n### Version\r\n3.2.4\r\n\r\n### Reproduction link\r\n[https://github.com/akibrk/custom-element-test/tree/css-issue](https://github.com/akibrk/custom-element-test/tree/css-issue)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\nClone the repo - \r\n\r\n1. `npm run install`\r\n2. `npm run build`\r\n3. copy the output from dist into demo directory\r\n4. run `npx http-server`\r\n\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\nOutput with file path resolved, and img and css folders alongside the output files. \r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\nPath is not being resolved, no css/img folders generated.\r\n\r\n---\r\nCustom elements with static assets. Not able to load assets from node_modules.\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "scope: custom elements"
  ],
